Heart and Affection, and made to walk in
a peaceable and quiet State, as the Wo|man
was<NOTE N="19" PLACE="foot">Mark Ch. <HI>v.</HI> v. 34.</NOTE> <HI>bid to go in Peace;</HI> if the
Church &s;hould then <HI>come behind</HI> Je&s;us
