and rightly touch by Faith, and appre|hend
<PB N="26" REF="33">
his<NOTE N="21" PLACE="foot">Ve&s;timenta Je&s;u &s;unt Sermones &amp; Scripta Evangeliorum. <HI>Origen in Matt. Ch.</HI> xvii.</NOTE> Garments or Words of Pro|phecy,
about which Chri&s;tians have hi|therto
