<NOTE N="32" PLACE="foot">Sed ne&s;ciebat Archi-Synagogus vel hoc vel illud multo excellentius &s;acramentum, quod Sab|bato curando Dominus intimabat, quia &s;cilicet po&s;t &s;ex hujus &s;eculi Aetates perpetuae Vitae immortalis erat gaudia daturus, <HI>Venerab. Bed. in Loc.</HI></NOTE> the My&s;tery. What may be &s;aid to
