<P><HI>Arnobius</HI><NOTE N="33" PLACE="foot">Ante Chri&s;tum in cogniti &amp; a &s;olo &s;ciento detecti. <HI>In Lib.</HI> II. <HI>adv. G$ntes.</HI></NOTE> &s;ays, <HI>That before Chri&s;t,
