<PB N="45" REF="52">
and &s;et at<NOTE N="39" PLACE="foot">Quamdiu vera Pax veniat, &amp; Sabbati&s;mus, &amp; Septem decadarum. Numerus.&mdash;Eccle&s;ia non plenam recipiat Libertatem. <HI>Sancti. Hieron. in Zechar. Ch.</HI> i.</NOTE> <HI>perfect Liberty</HI> again&s;t the
