<NOTE N="44" PLACE="foot">Diaboli Forman a&s;&s;umimus&mdash;Leonis Per|&s;onam induimus &amp; Draconis,&mdash;quando crudeles &amp; callidi &s;umus. <HI>Origen. in Luc. Hom.</HI> viii.</NOTE> which, for its <HI>Aver&s;ene&s;s</HI> to Liberty,
is called <HI>Satan;</HI> for its <HI>Calumnies,</HI> is cal|led
