the latter End of the <HI>&s;ixth Age</HI> of the
World, give the Woman of the Church
to under&s;tand <HI>all that &s;he has done,</HI> ac|cording
to the Writings of <HI>Mo&s;es</HI> and the
Prophets, who, upon the Te&s;timony of
the Fathers, have written a prophetical
Hi&s;tory of her, in Types, Symbols and
Parables; which Under&s;tanding of the
Things that have been prophecy'd of her,
will enable her, of Con&s;equence, to prove
