according to<NOTE N="62" PLACE="foot">In Locum Johan. Evang.</NOTE> <HI>Origen</HI> and
<NOTE N="63" PLACE="foot">Quinque enim Viros habui&s;ti, &amp; nunc quem habes <HI>non e&s;t Vir tuus.</HI> Sed non &s;unt haec carna|$iter accipienda, ne huic ip&s;i Mulieri Samaritanae &s;imiles videamur,&mdash;Per quinque Viros, quinqu. Libros Mo&s;is Nonnulli accipiunt&mdash;&s;ed quinque Viri in $word$ quinque Corporis &s;en&s;us. Et quia naturales &s;unt ip&s;i Sen&s;us, qui aetatem primam re|gunt, recte dicuntur Mariti. <HI>In Quae&s;t. 64. de</HI> lxxxiii. <HI>Quae&s;t.</HI></NOTE> St. <HI>Augu&s;tin,</HI> and others, how &s;he
