<P>La&s;tly, <HI>Je&s;us</HI>'s Di&s;ciples, <HI>v.</HI> 27. are &s;aid
<HI>to Marvel that he talk'd with the Wo|man.</HI>
What in the Name of Wonder, li|terally,
could be the Meaning of this?
Did they <HI>Marvel</HI> at <HI>Je&s;us's</HI> Conde&s;cention
to &s;peak to a Woman, as if the Sex was
