<PB N="62" REF="69">
apply'd. St. <HI>Augu&s;tin</HI><NOTE N="65" PLACE="foot">Magna quidem acta &s;unt Sacramenta, &s;ed angu&s;tum Tempus e&s;t, ut omnia pertractentur. <HI>In Serm.</HI> XCI. <HI>Sect.</HI> 2.</NOTE> &s;ays there are
&s;o many great My&s;teries contai$'d in it,
